About the Album

Welcome to the CityU Album! Here we showcase our diversified campus life, our cutting-edge facilities and snapshots of special moments at CityU.

We are pleased to share these unique moments with you. But please acknowledge CityU if you use any of the images, and please don’t use them for commercial purposes. If you have any questions, please contact us at cpro@cityu.edu.hk.
